          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"rectification-of-a-skew-semistandard-tableau-reactive-button-version\">Rectification of a skew semistandard tableau \u2014 REACTIVE BUTTON VERSION</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">English notation is used: rows increase downward and columns increase to\nthe right. Ordinary Young diagrams are top-left justified.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Choose a blue starting hole. During a slide there is no further choice:\npress <strong>next</strong> until the slide stops. Then the next set of possible\nstarting holes is recomputed from the new tableau.</span></span>"
